  "body": "Geth version: 1.4.11-stable\nOS & Version: Ubuntu\n#### Expected behaviour\n\neth_getFilterChanges should return error if filter is missing.\n#### Actual behaviour\n\nAs written here https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/2989#issuecomment-246003403 eth_getFilterChanges should return error if filter is missing in memory, so I can handle this error and create new filter, but if there is no filter in memory (you can try random filter hex) method still returns empty array, not error.\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\nRequest eth_getFilterChanges with random filter hex.\n",
